title: Total vehicles entering Canada in Canada 2019
summary: The Number of Total Canada entering to the Canada begins at a prominent high level , followed by a dramatical drop to reach the lowest point in April , which reduces to a fifth of the beginning point .
Then the Number remains stable with a slight increase to December .
gold: A line chart showing the total number of vehicles entering Canada for each month in 2019 . The number of vehicles entering Canada starts at around 2 million in January and increases to just below 3.6 million in August . In the next month , the value plummets to 2.8 million and continues to decrease through to the end of the year .
